      <div class="hls ps7" style="line-height:4.44mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0mm;top:54.91mm;height:5.29mm;width:159.99mm;"><span class="hrt cs26">01</span></div>
      <div class="hls ps5" style="line-height:2.66mm;white-space:nowrap;left:10.58mm;top:56.06mm;height:3.39mm;width:149.41mm;"><span class="hrt cs4">다음 문장을 논리적 순서대로 알맞게 배열한 것은?</span></div>
      <div class="hls ps5" style="line-height:43.65mm;white-space:nowrap;left:10.58mm;top:63.08mm;height:43.65mm;width:149.41mm;">
        <div class="htb" style="left:0mm;width:149.30mm;top:0mm;height:43.65mm;display:inline-block;position:relative;vertical-align:middle;">
          <svg class="hs" viewBox="-2.50 -2.50 154.30 48.64" style="left:-2.50mm;top:-2.50mm;width:154.30mm;height:48.64mm;">
            <path d="M0,0 L0,43.65" style="stroke:#787878;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-width:0.12;"></path>
