              <div class="hcI">
                <div class="hls ps4" style="line-height:2.48mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0mm;top:-0.16mm;height:3.17mm;width:143.30mm;"><span class="hrt cs1">∙</span><span class="hrt cs1">&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs1">갑 :&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs7">‘</span><span class="hrt cs1">을</span><span class="hrt cs7">’</span><span class="hrt cs1">은 화분을 깨뜨리지 않았다.</span></div>
                <div class="hls ps4" style="line-height:2.48mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0mm;top:4.77mm;height:3.17mm;width:143.30mm;"><span class="hrt cs1">∙</span><span class="hrt cs1">&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs1">을 : 화분을 깨뜨린 사람은&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs7">‘</span><span class="hrt cs1">정</span><span class="hrt cs7">’</span><span class="hrt cs1">이다.</span></div>
                <div class="hls ps4" style="line-height:2.48mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0mm;top:9.69mm;height:3.17mm;width:143.30mm;"><span class="hrt cs1">∙</span><span class="hrt cs1">&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs1">병 : 내가 깨뜨렸다.</span></div>
                <div class="hls ps4" style="line-height:2.48mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0mm;top:14.62mm;height:3.17mm;width:143.30mm;"><span class="hrt cs1">∙</span><span class="hrt cs1">&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs1">정 :&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs7">‘</span><span class="hrt cs1">을</span><span class="hrt cs7">’</span><span class="hrt cs1">의 말은 거짓말이다.</span></div>
                <div class="hls ps4" style="line-height:2.48mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0mm;top:19.54mm;height:3.17mm;width:143.30mm;"><span class="hrt cs1">∙</span><span class="hrt cs1">&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs1">무 : 나는 깨뜨리지 않았다.</span></div>
