                <div class="hls ps4" style="line-height:2.48mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0mm;top:4.77mm;height:3.17mm;width:153.80mm;"><span class="hrt cs1">∙</span><span class="hrt cs1">&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs1">회의에 참석한 남직원과 여직원의 비는 3</span><span class="hrt cs1">&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs1">:</span><span class="hrt cs1">&nbsp;</span><span class="hrt cs1">2이다.</span></div>
