      <div class="hls ps5" style="line-height:2.66mm;white-space:nowrap;left:10.58mm;top:203.09mm;height:3.39mm;width:149.41mm;"><span class="hrt cs4">B는 경찰이다.</span></div>
      <div class="hls ps21" style="line-height:2.63mm;white-space:nowrap;left:10.58mm;top:209.93mm;height:3.35mm;width:149.41mm;"><span class="hrt cs3">① 참</span><span class="htC" style="left:0.84mm;width:40.70mm;height:100%;"></span><span class="hrt cs3">② 거짓</span><span class="htC" style="left:0.84mm;width:37.81mm;height:100%;"></span><span class="hrt cs3">③ 알 수 없음</span></div>
