        <span class="hrt cs14">응용수리력</span></div>
      <div class="hls ps7" style="line-height:4.44mm;white-space:nowrap;left:0mm;top:9.58mm;height:5.29mm;width:159.99mm;"><span class="hrt cs26">01</span></div>
      <div class="hls ps5" style="line-height:2.66mm;white-space:nowrap;left:10.58mm;top:10.73mm;height:3.39mm;width:149.41mm;"><span class="hrt cs4">A와 B는 운전면허 시험에 도전하였다. B가 합격할 확률이 50%일 때, A와 B 모두 합격할 확률은 25%이다. A가&nbsp;</span></div>
      <div class="hls ps5" style="line-height:2.66mm;white-space:nowrap;left:10.58mm;top:15.81mm;height:3.39mm;width:149.41mm;"><span class="hrt cs4">불합격할 확률은?</span></div>
      <div class="hls ps3" style="line-height:7.26mm;white-space:nowrap;left:10.58mm;top:22.82mm;height:7.94mm;width:149.41mm;"><span class="hrt cs3">①</span>
        <div class="heq" style="width:4.01mm;height:7.94mm;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url('2편 최신기출문제 (46-143)_html_1224_hd106.png');display:inline-block;position:relative;vertical-align:middle;"></div>
